<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 18:08:44 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>加沙死亡人数正在改变拜登政府对以色列人质营救行动的基调</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/gaza-death-toll-is-changing-the-biden-administrations-tone-on-israels-rescue-operation/0000018f-fdb1-d660-af9f-fdbf6e000000</link><description>在美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯访问中东前夕，焦点从赞扬以色列救援行动转向承认巴勒斯坦平民伤亡并强调停火的必要性</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 17:44:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/gaza-death-toll-is-changing-the-biden-administrations-tone-on-israels-rescue-operation/0000018f-fdb1-d660-af9f-fdbf6e000000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列，第 247 天：获救的以色列人质与亲属分享被囚禁的故事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-247-rescued-israeli-hostages-share-stories-from-captivity-with-family/0000018f-fe06-d5ad-ad8f-fe4f16240000</link><description>在周六行动中获救的以色列人质与亲属分享被囚禁期间的故事 ■ 哈马斯控制的加沙卫生部：周六以色列袭击中至少 274 名巴勒斯坦人死亡，698 人受伤 ■ 以色列警方在特拉维夫抗议活动中逮捕 33 人，并暴力拘留医生 ■ 真主党称它首次向以色列发射 Falaq-2 火箭弹 ■ 这是战争进入 247 天后您需要了解的信息</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 17:40:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-247-rescued-israeli-hostages-share-stories-from-captivity-with-family/0000018f-fe06-d5ad-ad8f-fe4f16240000</guid></item><item><title>特拉维夫大学校长警告以色列拟议法律存在“麦卡锡主义”危险</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/tel-aviv-universitys-president-warns-of-mccarthyist-danger-of-proposed-israeli-law/0000018f-fd6e-de5e-a5ef-fdeeb9380000</link><description>以色列议会最近的一项法案要求大学立即解雇那些发表“反对以色列”或“支持恐怖”言论的讲师，特拉维夫大学校长呼吁“所有关心以色列民主本质的人”不要允许该法案通过。通过</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 15:30:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/tel-aviv-universitys-president-warns-of-mccarthyist-danger-of-proposed-israeli-law/0000018f-fd6e-de5e-a5ef-fdeeb9380000</guid></item><item><title>为什么加沙人质协议使虔诚的犹太人对犹太教的神圣教义产生分歧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-09/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-a-gaza-hostage-deal-is-dividing-religious-jews-about-a-sacred-tenant-of-judaism/0000018f-fc30-de5e-a5ef-fdb65dc50000</link><description>从布鲁克林到耶路撒冷，像我这样的极端正统犹太人一直在为人质祈祷和倡导，并且更喜欢外交而不是危险的救援任务。但我们的极端民族主义同行，包括伊塔马尔·本·格维尔，对事情的看法却截然不同</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 14:29:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-09/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-a-gaza-hostage-deal-is-dividing-religious-jews-about-a-sacred-tenant-of-judaism/0000018f-fc30-de5e-a5ef-fdb65dc50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列医生在特拉维夫抗议活动中遭到暴力逮捕，遭到立法者和医疗组织的批评</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/violent-arrest-of-israeli-doctor-at-tel-aviv-protest-draws-widespread-criticism/0000018f-fcac-db9d-addf-fdac78b90000</link><description>随着以色列警方对每周抗议活动的反应变得越来越暴力，以色列多个城市逮捕了超过 35 人 ■ 司法部调查机构对医生逮捕展开正式调查，以色列反对派领导人表示，对警察的行为“没有解释”</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 14:10:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/violent-arrest-of-israeli-doctor-at-tel-aviv-protest-draws-widespread-criticism/0000018f-fcac-db9d-addf-fdac78b90000</guid></item><item><title>在加沙获救的以色列人质的父亲在与儿子团聚前​​几小时去世</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/father-of-rescued-israeli-hostage-held-in-gaza-dies-hours-before-reuniting-with-son/0000018f-fce8-dd57-abbf-feeacd370000</link><description>获救人质阿尔莫格·梅厄·扬 (Almog Meir Jan) 的阿姨说：“大脑无法理解事情就是这样展开的，也无法理解事情就是这样结束的。”</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 13:31:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/father-of-rescued-israeli-hostage-held-in-gaza-dies-hours-before-reuniting-with-son/0000018f-fce8-dd57-abbf-feeacd370000</guid></item><item><title>获救以色列人质：“我们最害怕的是以色列飞机”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/rescued-israeli-hostage-our-greatest-fear-was-israeli-planes/0000018f-fcce-db9d-addf-fdce7ea20000</link><description>《国土报》采访了前以色列人质路易斯·哈尔，他于二月份被以色列军队从加沙救出。 “我可以告诉你，那里就是地狱”</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 13:24:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/rescued-israeli-hostage-our-greatest-fear-was-israeli-planes/0000018f-fcce-db9d-addf-fdce7ea20000</guid></item><item><title>因人质营救而推迟后，以色列甘茨宣布退出内塔尼亚胡政府</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/after-delay-due-to-hostage-rescue-gantz-expected-to-announce-exit-from-netanyahu-govt/0000018f-fca1-d93d-abbf-feb3ed5d0000</link><description>原定于周六举行的新闻发布会——本尼·甘茨部长为退出政府设定的最后期限，以免哈马斯后加沙政府的计划获得批准——在四名以色列人质从加沙获救的消息传出后被推迟到周日</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 11:56:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/after-delay-due-to-hostage-rescue-gantz-expected-to-announce-exit-from-netanyahu-govt/0000018f-fca1-d93d-abbf-feb3ed5d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列残奥会网球选手在罗兰·加洛斯赢得首个大满贯冠军</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-paralympic-tennis-player-wins-first-grand-slam-title-in-roland-garros/0000018f-fc4b-d5ad-ad8f-fc4bd55e0000</link><description>盖伊·萨森（Guy Sasson）在四人轮椅轮椅组单打比赛中排名世界第三，击败了排名第二的萨姆·施罗德（Sam Schröder）。萨森表示，他的胜利属于以色列，并将其献给在周六的救援任务中被释放的四名人质</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 10:28:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-paralympic-tennis-player-wins-first-grand-slam-title-in-roland-garros/0000018f-fc4b-d5ad-ad8f-fc4bd55e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列频道因对获救人质的出现发表不敏感言论而解雇主播</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/israeli-channel-fires-anchor-after-insensitive-comments-about-rescued-hostages-appearance/0000018f-fc17-d93d-abbf-fe377a200000</link><description>“看她的眉毛，比我的好看！”阿拉伯以色列电视节目主持人拉马·塔图尔 (Lama Tatour) 在 Instagram 上发帖，提到了诺亚·阿格马尼 (Noa Argmani) 的外貌，她在被哈马斯囚禁九个月后在人质营救行动中被释放</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 09:49:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/israeli-channel-fires-anchor-after-insensitive-comments-about-rescued-hostages-appearance/0000018f-fc17-d93d-abbf-fe377a200000</guid></item><item><title>将哈马斯领导人驱逐出卡塔尔并不会让辛瓦尔同意加沙停火协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/expelling-hamas-leaders-from-qatar-wont-make-sinwar-agree-to-a-gaza-cease-fire-deal/0000018f-fc03-df2e-a5df-fe7735240000</link><description>将哈马斯领导人驱逐出他们在卡塔尔的舒适避难所可能是一种严厉的个人惩罚，但这不太可能对加沙的辛瓦尔产生影响。如果哈尼亚有真正的影响力，那就是替代政府，而不是哈尼亚在卡塔尔享有的“保障性住房”</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 09:24:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/expelling-hamas-leaders-from-qatar-wont-make-sinwar-agree-to-a-gaza-cease-fire-deal/0000018f-fc03-df2e-a5df-fe7735240000</guid></item><item><title>哥伦比亚因加沙战争暂停向以色列出口煤炭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/colombia-to-suspend-coal-exports-to-israel-over-war-in-gaza/0000018f-fbea-d93d-abbf-fbfb582b0000</link><description>尽管依赖以色列武器，哥伦比亚总统仍将煤炭出口与结束以色列-加沙战争联系起来，同时呼吁其他国家效仿</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 08:26:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/colombia-to-suspend-coal-exports-to-israel-over-war-in-gaza/0000018f-fbea-d93d-abbf-fbfb582b0000</guid></item><item><title>对于以色列人来说不幸的是，内塔尼亚胡只有在有好消息时才会出现</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/unfortunately-for-israelis-netanyahu-only-shows-up-when-theres-good-news/0000018f-f96c-d084-abef-ff6d2db20000</link><description>当以色列军队大胆营救人质时，内塔尼亚胡出现在每张照片中，并在每台电视上发表讲话。但正如一名死去人质的父亲雄辩而悲惨地说的那样，“当结局不好时，首相就不会出现。”他也不打电话”</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 02:59:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/unfortunately-for-israelis-netanyahu-only-shows-up-when-theres-good-news/0000018f-f96c-d084-abef-ff6d2db20000</guid></item><item><title>“内塔尼亚胡阻止真正的胜利”：本尼·甘茨在八个月后退出政府</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article-live/police-use-water-cannons-make-arrests-at-tel-aviv-protest-calling-for-hostage-deal/0000018f-fab3-d3fb-a1af-ffbb4ead0000</link><description>美国国家安全顾问表示，美国没有参与以色列人质营救行动，拒绝透露情报相关细节 ■ 也门胡塞武装称，他们用弹道导弹瞄准了红海的英国驱逐舰“钻石”号 ■ 以色列特种部队军官在营救任务中身亡行动 ■ 美国恢复通过人道主义码头向加沙运送援助物资 ■ 哈马斯报告加沙中部有 200 多人丧生</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 02:22:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article-live/police-use-water-cannons-make-arrests-at-tel-aviv-protest-calling-for-hostage-deal/0000018f-fab3-d3fb-a1af-ffbb4ead0000</guid></item><item><title>从加沙解救四名人质对厌倦战争的以色列人来说是一记强心针，但远未达到“全面胜利”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/rescue-of-four-hostages-from-gaza-a-greatly-needed-shot-in-the-arm-for-war-weary-israelis/0000018f-f97b-df2e-a5df-ff7f10670000</link><description>虽然这一成就肯定会鼓舞仍在加沙作战的以色列国防军士兵的斗志，但这并不预示着战争方式的战略改变 — — 并可能导致哈马斯在停火谈判中加强其要求</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 21:57:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/rescue-of-four-hostages-from-gaza-a-greatly-needed-shot-in-the-arm-for-war-weary-israelis/0000018f-f97b-df2e-a5df-ff7f10670000</guid></item><item><title>美国向以色列提供营救人质情报，但参与程度尚不清楚</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/u-s-provided-intelligence-to-israel-for-hostage-rescue-but-involvement-is-unclear/0000018f-f943-de5e-a5ef-fdc7ef1b0000</link><description>以色列和美国官员指出，美国参与了以色列在加沙的人质营救任务的情报收集，但声称显示援助卡车和作为行动一部分的美国建造的码头的图像招致了批评，因为人质交易的未来已成定局。在空中</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 21:08:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/u-s-provided-intelligence-to-israel-for-hostage-rescue-but-involvement-is-unclear/0000018f-f943-de5e-a5ef-fdc7ef1b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列官员不确定救援行动将如何影响与哈马斯的谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/unclear-whether-rescue-will-aid-or-delay-deal-to-free-remaining-hostages/0000018f-f94b-dc3c-a9cf-f97fec3b0000</link><description>以色列和调解员正在等待哈马斯对乔·拜登提出的“以色列计划”的正式回应，消息人士称哈马斯的“同意”将对本杰明·内塔尼亚胡施加巨大压力</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 20:07:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/unclear-whether-rescue-will-aid-or-delay-deal-to-free-remaining-hostages/0000018f-f94b-dc3c-a9cf-f97fec3b0000</guid></item><item><title>获救的以色列人质诺亚·阿加玛尼与身患绝症的母亲团聚</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/rescued-israeli-hostage-noa-argamani-reunited-with-her-terminally-ill-mother/0000018f-f909-df2e-a5df-ff7d532c0000</link><description>哈马斯上周发布的一段视频中可以听到诺亚·阿加马尼 (Noa Argamani) 的声音，八个月后，周六，他与另外三名人质在以色列的一次行动中从加沙获救。</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 19:08:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/rescued-israeli-hostage-noa-argamani-reunited-with-her-terminally-ill-mother/0000018f-f909-df2e-a5df-ff7d532c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列各地数万人抗议，呼吁达成人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/tens-of-thousands-protest-across-israel-call-for-govt-to-accept-hostage-deal/0000018f-f90b-dc3c-a9cf-f93f2bcf0000</link><description>周六晚上，以色列各地爆发了抗议活动，在场人士呼吁达成协议，归还剩余 120 名人质并提前举行选举。警方在海法驱散反战抗议者，并在特拉维夫逮捕了33名反战抗议者</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 18:56:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/tens-of-thousands-protest-across-israel-call-for-govt-to-accept-hostage-deal/0000018f-f90b-dc3c-a9cf-f93f2bcf0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列大胆救援行动证明：人质还活着，只有达成协议才能拯救他们</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/israels-rescue-operation-proves-hostages-are-still-alive-only-a-deal-will-save-them/0000018f-f8de-d084-abef-fedfc8280000</link><description>本杰明·内塔尼亚胡周六赶到示巴医院与被释放的人质合影，但他尚未会见上周宣布死亡的人质家属。与此同时，总理的喉舌已经在利用救援行动来抹黑领导人的竞争对手</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 18:34:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/israels-rescue-operation-proves-hostages-are-still-alive-only-a-deal-will-save-them/0000018f-f8de-d084-abef-fedfc8280000</guid></item></channel></rss>